    "answer": null,
    "explanation": "<p>We know that</p>\n<p>$$\\tan \\theta \\tan \\left(90^{\\circ}-\\theta\\right)=\\tan \\theta \\cdot \\cot \\theta=1$$</p>\n<p>$$\\tan 1^{\\circ} \\tan 89^{\\circ}=\\tan 2^{\\circ} \\tan 88^{\\circ}=\\tan 3^{\\circ} \\tan 87^{\\circ} =\\tan 44^{\\circ} \\tan 46^{\\circ}=1$$</p>\n<p>So, $$\\log _{10} \\tan 1^{\\circ}+\\log _{10} \\tan 2^{\\circ} \\ldots \\log _{10} \\tan 89^{\\circ}$$</p>\n<p>$$=\\left(\\log _{10} \\tan 1^{\\circ}+\\log _{10} \\tan 89^{\\circ}\\right) +  \\left(\\log _{10} \\tan 2^{\\circ}+\\log _{10} \\tan 88^{\\circ}\\right) +\\ldots+\\left(\\log _{10} \\tan 44^{\\circ}\\right.  \\left.+\\log _{10} \\tan 46^{\\circ}\\right) \\\\\n +\\log _{10} \\tan 45^{\\circ}$$</p>\n<p>$$=\\log _{10}\\left(\\tan 1^{\\circ}+\\tan 89^{\\circ}\\right)+\\log _{10}\\left(\\tan 2^{\\circ}+\\tan 88^{\\circ}\\right) +\\ldots+\\log _{10}\\left(\\tan 44^{\\circ}+\\tan 46^{\\circ}\\right) +\\log _{10} \\tan 45^{\\circ}=\\log _{10} 1+\\ldots+\\log _{10} 1+\\log _{10} 1$$</p>\n<p>$$=0$$</p>\n<p>Thus, $$e^{\\left.e \\log _{10} \\tan 1^{\\circ}+\\log _{10} \\tan 2^{\\circ}+\\ldots+\\log _{10} \\tan 89^{\\circ}\\right)}$$</p>\n<p>$$=e^0=1$$</p>",
